Package: tevt
Type: Package
Title: Threshold Methods for Extreme Value Theory
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kieran", "Molloy", email = "k.molloy@lancs.ac.uk",
                role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Threshold Estimation methods for generalised Pareto Distributions (GPD), most are based upon reducing the bias of the GPD or minimising AMSE.
